title: Avengers Initiative
bio: Earth's Mightiest Heroes unite to protect the world from threats too big for any one hero to handle alone.

title: Guardians of the Galaxy
bio: A ragtag team of intergalactic misfits sworn to protect the galaxy from cosmic threats.

title: X-Men: School for Gifted Youngsters
bio: A sanctuary for mutants to learn, grow, and fight for peaceful coexistence between humans and mutants.

title: Justice League
bio: The world's premier superhero team, dedicated to protecting Earth and upholding justice across the universe.

title: Fantastic Four
bio: A family of heroes with incredible powers, exploring the unknown and protecting the world from fantastic threats.

title: Teen Titans
bio: Young heroes coming together to fight crime and learn what it means to be a team.

title: The Bat-Family
bio: Gotham's protectors working in the shadows to keep the city safe from its darkest threats.

title: S.H.I.E.L.D. Academy
bio: Strategic Homeland Intervention, Enforcement and Logistics Division - protecting the world from extraordinary threats.

title: Cosmic Defenders
bio: Heroes who protect the universe from cosmic-level threats and maintain balance across the multiverse.

title: Young Justice
bio: The next generation of heroes proving themselves worthy of the legacy they inherit.
